= Linebook

Cookbooks for {Linecook}[http://gemcutter.org/gems/linecook].

== Description

Linebook is a distribution module used by
{Linecook}[http://gemcutter.org/gems/linecook]. Linebook aggregates files from
multiple directories and generates a manifest for lookup using relative paths.

== Usage

Given these files:

  /pwd/lib/one.rb
  /gem/a/lib/two.rb
  /gem/b/lib/three.rb

Linebook generates a manifest by specifying the paths and patterns to glob:

  Linebook('patterns' => 'lib/*/**.rb', 'paths' => '/pwd', 'gems' => 'a:b')
  # => {
  #   'one.rb'   => '/pwd/lib/one.rb', 
  #   'two.rb'   => '/gem/a/lib/two.rb',
  #   'three.rb' => '/gem/b/lib/three.rb'
  # }

See Linebook for config details.

== Installation

Linebook is available as a gem on {Gemcutter}[http://gemcutter.org/gems/linebook]

  % gem install linebook

